          <unitName xml:lang="en">EUR2005</unitName>
          <comment xml:lang="en">This price is based on an average price from 2019 to 2022 data collected from the ISE database. The price is calculated considering the incoterm:FOB Last access: October 2023 The prices were converted to EUR based on the annual exchange rates published by the European Central Bank (https://sdw.ecb.europa.eu/quickview.do?SERIES_KEY=120.EXR.A.USD.EUR.SP00.A, last accessed on 2023-06-01) and adjusted for inflation relative to 2005 using the producer price index (PPI) of the euro area, published by eurostat (https://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/databrowser/view/STS_INPP_A__custom_6416181/default/table?lang=en, last accessed on 2023-06-01).</comment>
